    "description": {
      "value": "<div><hr /><div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You've learned to put the weight of a weapon to your advantage, letting its momentum empower your strikes. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">On your turn, when you score a critical hit with a melee weapon or reduce a creature to 0 hit points with one, you can make one melee weapon attack as a bonus action.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">Before you make a melee attack with a heavy weapon that you are proficient with, you can choose to take a -5 penalty to the attack roll. If the attack hits, you add +10 to the attack's damage.</li></ul></div>\n\t\t\t</div></div>",
